ji\" /> <br />\n咁是但一個部門ACO，是但其他唔關事AO/EO都入得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1500aae43e2295061d46bb1bdd1f6aafa3f8c60d","tid":442744,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勞</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">資</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"284a92c15141b91976e07a4801ca5a5a16d857ff","tid":442744,"uid":17623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"Lift shaft 未起完<br />\n唔洗登記都入得 <br />\n未必裝左臨時閘<br />\n但有中高欄 <br />\n外邊跌入去可能性低<br />\n照佢講 打炮既 <br />\n係lift shaft 做<br />\n一係樓上拆板比木枋打中<br />\n不過正常好小發生<br />\n因為佢拆板施工方法有問題<br />\n廿層高 掉落下邊一定比人屌到仆街<br />\n但新聞話有雜物扎住<br />\n奇怪<br />\n一係打炮企架外失足跌出去 無扣安全帶<br />\n廿層高跌落去 <br />\n唔明點解有人消失左d伙記判頭唔知"},{"pid":"0425b313b7da67eb44b0290e7fe62df896b79cd9","tid":442744,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>惟地盤人員基於安全起見，未讓家人及親友入內。<br />\n好正路<br />\n但慈母又唔會入去睇嘅?</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要上安全堂拎綠卡先</span><br />\n你玉皇大帝黎到都要有卡先入得</blockquote><br />\n慈母，救護員同消防員係唔洗㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">公務員全部唔使架</span><br />\n註冊工程師都唔需要<br />\n<br />\n返去上重溫堂啦</blockquote><br />\n邊個咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n公務員全部唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁是但一個部門ACO，是但其他唔關事AO/EO都入得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n送貨佬咪一樣無卡,咪又係照入,唔畀入無問題呀,班懶撚唔肯自己搬咪又係放人入去"},{"pid":"61413b3d11adf96934a8dc4ea46aa1e29bf20ab4","tid":442744,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17b0dad33212b61ab32717baf205bcabac471d4","tid":442744,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"樓上嗰啲用下腦<br />\n下下要綠卡先畀入地盤<br />\n出左事個傷者係唔係由其他工友抬出去畀救護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91d7581c41d4d11d5868848db1690556334e771","tid":442744,"uid":46300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lift shaft 未起完<br />\n唔洗登記都入得 <br />\n未必裝左臨時閘<br />\n但有中高欄 <br />\n外邊跌入去可能性低<br />\n照佢講 打炮既 <br />\n係lift shaft 做<br />\n一係樓上拆板比木枋打中<br />\n不過正常好小發生<br />\n因為佢拆板施工方法有問題<br />\n廿層高 掉落下邊一定比人屌到仆街<br />\n但新聞話有雜物扎住<br />\n奇怪<br />\n一係打炮企架外失足跌出去 無扣安全帶<br />\n廿層高跌落去 <br />\n唔明點解有人消失左d伙記判頭唔知</blockquote><br />\n話個阿伯係臨時開工 可能d伙記都唔知佢有返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269a74461fb6e3625b698d67228204cd9c49dcb6","tid":442744,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警方在家人報案翌日(18日，周三)出動機動部隊人員及警犬在地盤一帶搜尋，惟未有發現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點撚會知係槽底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}